    "34",
    "(1) Brak ne mogu zaključiti među sobom svekar i snaha, zet i tašta, očuh i pastorka i maćeha i pastorak, bez obzira na to da li je prestao brak usljed čijeg su zaključenja došli u to srodstvo. (2) Iz opravdanih razloga sud može u vanparničnom postupku dozvoliti zaključenje braka srodnicima po tazbini iz stava 1. ovog člana. (3) Prije donošenja odluke iz stava 1. ovog člana, sud pribavlja mišljenje organa starateljstva.",
    "(1) A father-in-law and daughter-in-law, son-in-law and mother-in-law, stepfather and stepdaughter, and stepmother and stepson cannot marry each other, regardless of whether the marriage has ended due to which they have entered into that kinship. (2) For justified reasons, the court may permit, in a non-contentious procedure, the marriage of relatives by affinity referred to in paragraph 1 of this article. (3) Before making a decision from paragraph 1 of this article, the court obtains the opinion of the guardianship authority.",
