    "Če je več oseb skupaj dolžnih koga preživljati, se ta dolžnost razdeli mednje po njihovih zmožnostih in tudi glede na to, koliko je bil kdo deležen skrbi in pomoči.",
    "If several persons are jointly obligated to support someone, that obligation is divided among them according to their abilities and also in consideration of how much each has contributed to care and assistance.",
